      • loadConfigAsClasspathResource

        public static void loadConfigAsClasspathResource(boolean loadAsResource)
        Where should the WordNetManager load its configuration file from. If this function is given a paramter true, then it looks for the file in the classpath. Otherwise, it looks for it in the file system. The default option is to look for it in the classpath.
